      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including an engine that requires a complete overhaul and a transmission that is slipping badly. The exterior shows heavy wear with several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior has multiple tears in the upholstery and a broken climate control system. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for spare parts, but it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
